    <note>Lu(9) Zhen [1292] Jinshi # 1. The family's ancestral home was Jiangning, Jiangning and his grandfather, Yu [15515], moved the family's ancestral registers to Yangzhou, Jiangdu xian. Yu served in a minor office in Huizhou, and I will date the move to Huizhou with his son, Wenzhong [3659], Zhen's great uncle, who, received his jinshi under the Southern Tang and was involved in the compilation of the Taiping yulan and the Wenyuan yinghua. Wenzhong's address was Huizhou, Xixian. The maternal grandfather of Zhen's wife was Zheng(1) Wenbao [428]. XCB, 169.4a; HSSCGY, 4.8b; Ouyang Xiu, WJ, 28.5b; SS, 320.5a. CBD, 2, 1118-9.</note>
